text.tspan: Experience of Christ â€” As Grace
Grace that was prophesied in ancient times,
Is to our hearts so dear.
The grace of life to the saints, strong and weak,
His divine Trinity flowing is grace,
The varied grace of God, riches of life,
Conveys the gracious, sweet words of Christ
Grace to the humble the Grace-giver gives,
Cast all your cares and fears onto God,
The God of all grace, the true grace of God,
Consummates into the City of Grace,
